  </div>

  <div class="m-two-five">

    <div class="vertical-center m-section__intro">
    <p>
      Computer science degrees are some of the most promising in terms of finding employment after graduation. These along with other STEM degrees offer the highest income and greatest flexibility. However, they are just not attracting the same (or even close) amount of woman and men.
    </p>
    <p>
      There is a serious lack of women within the tech industry — especially the start up scene. Some women may be deterred from the “boys' club” this industry has become, others might not be aware that these types of jobs exist at all. The truth remains the same: we need more women in tech and and there is no one solution.
    </p>
  </div>
