  <div id="issues">
  <h2>What's stopping them?</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="m-three">
      <p><strong>Issue #1:</strong>People actually believe that men have a genetic advantage in math and science related field.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="m-three">
      <p><strong>Issue #2:</strong> Because there are not many women in executive roles at tech companies, women are extremely underrepresented and some may not even realize these jobs are an option for them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="m-three">
      <p><strong>Issue #3:</strong> 44% of US women believe they have to act like a man to progress in the field.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
